text: Kupcheneyevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Sukkulovsky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 445 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Yermekeyevo, 7 km from Sukkulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Kupcheneyevo
